=Description=

Bobby Azarian:

"Neuromancy invites us to embark on a journey of self-discovery by creating cognitive agents — detailed mental models of individuals we admire and aspire to emulate that essentially take on a life of their own. By becoming aware of these inner companions we’ve mentally encoded, which reside mostly within the subconscious realm of our minds, we may be able to unlock new dimensions of our cognitive potential. In this article we will explore the art of crafting cognitive agents who can then be consciously exploited to optimize our decision-making and enhance productivity and creativity."

(https://roadtoomega.substack.com/p/introducing-neuromancy-enhancing)

